{"tid":797183,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"「集思廣益」女人去到30定35 個價值先會下降 先會定性玩夠？","createTime":"2018-08-28T10:16:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T09:12:44.000Z","uid":87155,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"382d2ab42c5d77c88ee40a17946f4c750dfd4e8c","tid":797183,"uid":87155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T10:16:43.000Z","msg":"一d又話去到30仲大把貨賣 一d又話35就會唔出去玩<br />\n<br />\n通常大部份女人出去玩都係覺得自己係deserve better 仲有大把價講 所以先未定性 <br />\n<br />\n但又話女人既價值會隨年齡不斷下降<br />\n<br />\n正常女人 全盛期20-30 無限派帽 偷食都得 但幾時先會完呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"424b680bf93fcd8a2276a13018f19773fe9ca81f","tid":797183,"uid":60686,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T10:22:40.000Z","msg":"25已經開始跌價啦 ching"},{"pid":"44f10fb167e2d0bff25189dfa7c45d58f9599f9a","tid":797183,"uid":87155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"424b680bf93fcd8a2276a13018f19773fe9ca81f","tid":797183,"uid":60686,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T10:22:40.000Z","msg":"25已經開始跌價啦 ching"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T10:23:45.000Z","msg":"唔撚係掛 識唔少25-27仲講緊去邊到蒲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bcb2ebca9ea9f3508113a02769da7507310b139","tid":797183,"uid":2267,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"44f10fb167e2d0bff25189dfa7c45d58f9599f9a","tid":797183,"uid":87155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"424b680bf93fcd8a2276a13018f19773fe9ca81f","tid":797183,"uid":60686,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T10:22:40.000Z","msg":"25已經開始跌價啦 ching"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T10:23:45.000Z","msg":"唔撚係掛 識唔少25-27仲講緊去邊到蒲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T10:36:15.000Z","msg":"識唔識分去浦同搵人埋啤嘅分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f96aadadea731f3642f8d77767933082a94c9fe7","tid":797183,